    <item>
      <title>德国称其国防开支可能增至GDP的3.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/germany-says-its-defense-spending-could-increase-to-3-5-of-gdp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国国防部长鲍里斯·皮斯托利斯表示，德国可能会将军费开支增加至经济产出的 3.5%，并加大投资力度，扭转多年来忽视武装部队的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/germany-says-its-defense-spending-could-increase-to-3-5-of-gdp</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 15:37:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最后抵制的匈牙利可能本月就瑞典的北约申办进行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/last-holdout-hungary-may-vote-this-month-on-sweden-s-nato-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利议会最早可能在本月批准瑞典加入北约的申请，此前该国推迟了一年多，最终导致瑞典加入北约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/last-holdout-hungary-may-vote-this-month-on-sweden-s-nato-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 15:19:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国王毅表示现在还不是谈论俄罗斯和乌克兰和平的时候</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/ukraine-seeks-to-meet-chinese-minister-to-discuss-peace-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外长王毅表示，通过和谈结束俄罗斯对乌克兰战争的条件还不成熟。乌克兰外长德米特罗·库莱巴(Dmytro Kuleba)一直在寻求周末会面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/ukraine-seeks-to-meet-chinese-minister-to-discuss-peace-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 11:20:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国和盟国希望用人工智能无人机武装乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/us-uk-may-arm-ukraine-with-ai-enabled-drones-to-target-russian-positions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，英国正在与包括美国在内的国家合作，向乌克兰提供数千架新型人工智能无人机，这些无人机可以同时攻击俄罗斯目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/us-uk-may-arm-ukraine-with-ai-enabled-drones-to-target-russian-positions</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 10:58:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰在俄罗斯压力下离开被围困的阿夫季夫卡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/ukraine-withdraws-from-embattled-avdiivka-under-russian-pressure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军方表示，经过数月的战斗，他们将从被围困的东部城市阿夫迪夫卡撤军，此举为快速推进的俄罗斯军队赢得了战场上的重大胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-17/ukraine-withdraws-from-embattled-avdiivka-under-russian-pressure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 17 Feb 2024 02:40:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经过四个月的战斗后，乌克兰军队从阿夫迪夫卡撤军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-16/russia-tightens-the-noose-on-ukraine-s-city-of-avdiivka-where-outnumbered-defenders-are-holding-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰基辅（美联社）——俄罗斯国防部周六表示，俄罗斯军队已完全控制乌克兰城市阿夫季夫卡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-02-16/russia-tightens-the-noose-on-ukraine-s-city-of-avdiivka-where-outnumbered-defenders-are-holding-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 11:21:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
